description: Intense look inside the world of junior college football, chronicling the stories of players and coaches in the classroom and on the field.

title: Diego Maradona
description: Constructed from over 500 hours of never-before-seen footage, this documentary centers on the career of celebrated football player Diego Maradona, who played for S.S.C. Napoli in the 1980s.

title: Flight/Risk
description: Everyday people find themselves in the midst of a global tragedy when two Boeing 737 Max planes crashed in 2018 and 2019. This documentary is told through the perspective of affected family members, their legal teams, and whistleblowers.

title: Keeper of the Ashes: The Oklahoma Girl Scout Murders
description: Award-winning actress and singer Kristin Chenoweth returns to her hometown to investigate Oklahoma's most infamous murders. Keeper of the Ashes is the true story of three young Oklahoma girls, found murdered after their first night at sleep-away camp. The tragedy, as well as the manhunt and trial of their suspected killer, captivated the nation in the summer of 1977. But decades later, uncertainties surrounding the case continue to haunt the Tulsa community, local law enforcement, and the victims' families.::Hulu

title: I'll Be Gone in the Dark
description: Gripping examination of the unsolved crimes of the Golden State Killer who terrorized California in the 1970s and 1980s.

title: 100 Foot Wave
description: Follows the decade-long odyssey of big-wave pioneer Garrett McNamara who, after visiting a small fishing village in Portugal, helped push the sport beyond the realm of imagination.

title: Seduced: Inside the NXIVM Cult
description: Seduced follows India Oxenberg's abuse and her own culpability inside the NXIVM cult, an organization marketed as a self-help group.

title: Le chÃªne
description: Follows many families who inhabit the oak like a home, living together as in a proper society, with problems with the neighbors, education, solidarity, survival, etc.

title: Paranormal Caught on Camera
description: A panel of experts analyze footage from some of the world's most eye-opening and terrifying paranormal videos. From poltergeist activity to lights in the sky, these firsthand accounts just might turn skeptics into believers.

title: Jeen-yuhs: A Kanye Trilogy
description: Follows the life of Kanye West, in an intimate portrait as he builds his way from singer to businessman and becomes a global brand.

title: Light & Magic
description: Showcasing the people of Industrial Light and Magic, the special effects division of Lucasfilm, this series takes us back in time as they create the effects for some of the biggest and most successful films of the last 45 years.

title: Hard Knocks
description: Hard Knocks is a reality sports documentary produced by the NFL and HBO. Each season the show follows an NFL team during training camp in preparation for the upcoming season.

title: The Velvet Queen
description: Two men explore the high-altitude wilderness of Tibet with many cameras, filming wildlife from a respectful distance and searching for the rare snow leopard.

title: Windy City Heat
description: A man caught up in the glamor of being a Hollywood celebrity has no idea that the production he's in is a fake.

title: Woodstock
description: Oscar-winning musical chronicle that brilliantly captures the three-day rock concert and celebration of peace and love that became a capstone for the Sixties.

title: Zeitgeist
description: Mythology and belief in society today, presenting uncommon perspectives of common cultural issues.

title: The Green Planet
description: Dive into a world where a single life can last a thousand years, with David Attenborough. See things no eye has ever seen, and discover the dramatic, beautiful plant life of Earth.

title: Amy
description: A family drama focused on three generations of women living together in Hartford, Connecticut.

title: The Circus: Inside the Greatest Political Show on Earth
description: Groundbreaking weekly docu-series that pulls back the curtain on American politics. Hosts John Heilemann, Mark McKinnon, Alex Wagner and Jenn Palmieri go behind the scenes for an unbiased, inside look at the stories beyond the headlines.

title: Capturing the Killer Nurse
description: This documentary reveals how investigators proved ICU nurse Charles Cullen was killing patients â and how close he came to getting away with murder.

title: Personality Crisis: One Night Only
description: Follow artist David Johansen's luminous set at CafÃ© Carlyle from January 2020. A concert that is wonderfully intimate and a testament to both a lost New York and an artist who remains as fresh and exciting as ever.

title: Violently Happy
description: A sensual and intimate experience about a group of postmodern Berliners, looking for new ways of living, loving and experimenting with sexual fantasies.

title: Web of Make Believe: Death, Lies and the Internet
description: Conspiracy. Fraud. Violence. Murder. What starts out virtual can get real all too quickly--and when the web is worldwide, so are the consequences.

title: Bondi Rescue
description: Harry loses his cool with 3 swimmers that he's forced to rescue just seconds after warning them not to swim in a dangerous area. However, calling them "imbeciles" and "idiots" puts him in hot water.

title: The Prophecy
description: At the scene of a bizarre murder, L.A. homicide detective Thomas Dagget discovers a lethal heavenly prophecy now being fulfilled on earth. In his fight to stop the forces of evil, he finds an unlikely ally in an elementary school teacher.

title: Master of Light
description: George Anthony Morton, a classical painter who spent ten years in federal prison travels to his hometown to paint his family members. Going back forces George to face his past in his quest to rewrite the script of his life.

title: I Just Killed My Dad
description: Anthony Templet shot his father and never denied it. But why he did it is a complex question with profound implications. Explore Anthony's psyche prior to the events of June 3, 2019 and the journey of his mental and emotional aftermath.

title: Sexology
description: Two famous actresses embark on a taboo-breaking quest to discover the secrets of the female orgasm.

title: Lucy and Desi
description: Follows Lucy and Desi as they face a crisis that could end their careers and another that could end their marriage.

title: The Triumph of the Will
description: The infamous propaganda film of the 1934 Nazi Party rally in Nuremberg, Germany.
